life 's whirlpool is a 1917 american silent drama film written and directed by lionel barrymore with his sister ethel barrymore as the star . this is the brother and sister 's only collaboration on a silent film as director and star . this film should not be confused with mcteague ( also known as life 's whirlpool ) , the first film adaptation of frank norris 's mcteague . the lionel barrymore directed film was produced by b. a. rolfe and released through metro pictures . barrymore would return for a short time to directing films in the early sound era . this is now considered to be a lost film .